description: This year's results in the Republic of Ireland are still expected to be significantly higher than previous.
title: Coronavirus: 17% of Leaving Cert grades predicted by school to be reduced
title_page: Coronavirus: 17% of Leaving Cert grades predicted by school to be reduced - BBC News
maintext: The department argued that had there been no grade reduction the number of grade ones awarded at Higher Level would have doubled in many subjects, and tripled in some, compared to previous years.
